and laser weapons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meat trees with toxic gases </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you see blood splattering around with every shot. You use different weapons to kill enemies. You can destroy enemies in groups by throwing grenades and shooting barrels and explosive gas capsules. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break wooden crates and loot chests and backpacks to collect ammo and health packs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/320.gif?t=1739100801\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Summary of the story of the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world has been destroyed by war and governments have fallen. Most of the regions of the earth have been contaminated with deadly gases, nuclear radiation and unknown diseases. People call these regions the awakening region. That is, the place where you must always be awake because if you sleep, you will not wake up again. You enter the game in the role of Yusuf, who is a former employee of the rescue forces. During the chaos a year ago, he lost his wife and child in one of the safe areas, and now a request for help from the awakening area brings him there, because he thinks that this help message was sent by his wife </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3031980?t=1739100801","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3031980?t=1739100801","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/8f5dcef65d2fc6c730c614a5967aa23f9ff5f3e1/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739100